About ASPA Dental Care Centre

Your Trusted Dental Partner in Bhandup West, Mumbai

Led by Dr. Lalit Ashok Manek (BDS, MDS - Prosthodontist), ASPA Dental Care Centre combines 20 years of expertise with compassionate care to deliver exceptional dental solutions. Our clinic is dedicated to advanced procedures, from cosmetic makeovers to implantology, ensuring every patient achieves a healthy, confident smile.

Services

Complete Preventive Care

From routine cleanings (Scaling/Polishing) to advanced diagnostics (Digital X-rays, Oral Lesions Screening), we stop problems before they start with sealants, fluoride treatments, and custom mouth guards.

Cosmetic Smile Transformations

Achieve red-carpet smiles through veneers (Porcelain/Laminates), whitening, and jewelry accents, complemented by gum contouring (Gingivoplasty) and complete smile makeovers.

Cosmetic Smile Transformations

Achieve red-carpet smiles through veneers (Porcelain/Laminates), whitening, and jewelry accents, complemented by gum contouring (Gingivoplasty) and complete smile makeovers.

Cosmetic Smile Transformations

Achieve red-carpet smiles through veneers (Porcelain/Laminates), whitening, and jewelry accents, complemented by gum contouring (Gingivoplasty) and complete smile makeovers.

Advanced Tooth Restoration

Choose from tooth-colored fillings, durable crowns (Zirconia/Ceramic), or precision bridges - including implant-supported options and same-day CEREC restorations.

Advanced Tooth Restoration

Choose from tooth-colored fillings, durable crowns (Zirconia/Ceramic), or precision bridges - including implant-supported options and same-day CEREC restorations.

Advanced Tooth Restoration

Choose from tooth-colored fillings, durable crowns (Zirconia/Ceramic), or precision bridges - including implant-supported options and same-day CEREC restorations.

Implant & Surgical Solutions

Comprehensive implant services from single teeth (Osseointegrated implants) to full-arch solutions with bone grafting and sinus lifts when needed, plus oral surgery (Extractions, Alveoloplasty).

Implant & Surgical Solutions

Comprehensive implant services from single teeth (Osseointegrated implants) to full-arch solutions with bone grafting and sinus lifts when needed, plus oral surgery (Extractions, Alveoloplasty).

Implant & Surgical Solutions

Comprehensive implant services from single teeth (Osseointegrated implants) to full-arch solutions with bone grafting and sinus lifts when needed, plus oral surgery (Extractions, Alveoloplasty).

Orthodontic Correction

Traditional metal/ceramic braces, clear aligners (Invisalign), and specialized treatments for jaw alignment (Orthopedics) with post-treatment retainers.

Orthodontic Correction

Traditional metal/ceramic braces, clear aligners (Invisalign), and specialized treatments for jaw alignment (Orthopedics) with post-treatment retainers.

Specialized Therapies

TMJ/TMD relief through occlusal splints, sleep apnea devices, cleft lip repair, and maxillofacial prosthetics for complex rehabilitation cases.

Specialized Therapies

Emergency & Comfort Care

Same-day treatment for pain (RCT), trauma, and broken restorations, with sedation options (Nitrous Oxide) for anxious patients.
